{
  "sections": {
    "gp_section_607866108799615543": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "6225802763a1da41e41b97b7e5a6f27efc49b379031d1db8985ec42d05a213f3_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg--bmUyAWR_text": "<p><i><strong>\"I can't take these. The side effects are worse than the disease.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "gg-WukyumMD_text": "<p>I was already behind, and nothing my doctor offered was actually going to rebuild what I'd lost.</p>",
        "gg1pxQC0j1t_text": "<p>And up until last year, I thought I was doing everything right for my bones.</p>",
        "gg3IHo5T8fp_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-a861d221-bbd7-4104-9367-da6e39311929_1.webp",
        "gg8oUuWeTXf_text": "<p><strong>What Dr. Chen Revealed</strong></p>",
        "gg9DhnOBEZ7_text": "<p>Dr. Chen explained it like this:</p>",
        "gg9KsRT63lF_text": "<p><i>\"Your lumbar spine T-score is negative 2.3. That's osteopenia, borderline osteoporosis.\"</i></p>",
        "ggChl48BMCR_text": "<p>I figured it would just confirm what I already knew. My bones were fine.</p>",
        "ggD3qdUjCsi_text": "<p><strong>Then I got the call...</strong></p>",
        "ggDNlcBdt2n_text": "<p><strong>The Real Reason Your Bones Are Crumbling</strong></p>",
        "ggEHEb0KhAl_text": "<p>I started reading and everything changed...</p>",
        "ggFPV1iBd01_text": "<p><i>\"Sometimes calcium and vitamin D aren't enough. We should really talk about medication. I'm going to prescribe Fosamax.\"</i></p>",
        "ggFiMephhWn_text": "<p>That's when I found an article by Dr. Marcus Chen.</p>",
        "ggGaL7z6cMQ_text": "<p>They start tearing down bone faster than the builders can replace it.</p>",
        "ggHUccDtm1b_text": "<p><i><strong>That's when I found that the real problem went far deeper than anyone wanted to admit.&nbsp;</strong></i></p>",
        "ggJCD2hw9-O_text": "<p>- Increased risk of blood clots</p>",
        "ggKDSMf1Y3__text": "<p><strong>I was terrified of fractures.</strong></p>",
        "ggKbYg0MGZo_text": "<p><i>\"But... how could this happen to me? I take calcium every single day. I'm too young for this. This doesn't make sense.\"</i></p>",
        "ggL4jqcc_69_text": "<p>Three weeks later, at 2 AM, I was still searching online.</p>",
        "ggNSyJBLOI6_text": "<p>My name is Sarah Martinez. I'm 53 years old.</p>",
        "ggNvbhlMSiq_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_hdksithdksithdks_1_05fb3ebe-b674-4754-8580-9d3494b3698c.webp",
        "ggO1opcaY-C_text": "<p><i><strong>&nbsp;(And Why It Made My Blood Boil)</strong></i></p>",
        "ggOWlAulHIM_text": "<p><strong>Atypical femur fractures. Your thigh bone just snaps in half while you're walking.</strong></p>",
        "ggOkg6s9cqf_text": "<p><strong>The Phone Call That Changed Everything</strong></p>",
        "ggP4j7J7e_w_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_brsvb0brsvb0brsv.png",
        "ggPG6VKxBFZ_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#E51B09;\"><i><strong>Osteoclasts </strong></i></span><i>- These break down old bone. Think of them as the demolition crew.</i></p>",
        "ggPU6l6XnDl_text": "<p><i>\"Then I don't know what else to tell you, Sarah. Just keep taking your calcium.\"</i></p>",
        "ggRPpadh1N8_text": "<p><strong>My doctor always said I was a model patient.</strong></p>",
        "ggSbCM100BX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jz3fwnjz3fwnjz3f_1.webp",
        "ggSzx4DLUSK_text": "<p>- Breast cancer concerns</p>",
        "ggTgqGUtPrQ_text": "<p>Here's what Dr. Chen wrote. I'm sharing it word-for-word because every woman needs to hear this:</p>",
        "ggUFWQvipEE_text": "<p><strong>But during menopause, everything goes haywire.</strong></p>",
        "ggUL5Q33ZMr_text": "<p>I sat down hard in my kitchen chair.</p>",
        "ggUX5O7bPg__text": "<p><strong>My doctor was quiet for a moment.</strong></p>",
        "ggUe7qoKskn_text": "<p><strong>I took calcium citrate, vitamin D3, and K2 every single morning for eight years... Never missed a day.</strong></p>",
        "ggXowyMtCXP_text": "<p>The headline stopped me cold:</p>",
        "ggXtTSpPxzz_text": "<p>Most people would assume an easy fix is to raise estrogen levels…</p>",
        "gg_h51Bqcwy_text": "<p>I didn't want to be rushed into making a very consequential decision, so I did what anyone would do.</p>",
        "gga-ptiUaW2_text": "<p>Your bones have two types of cells:</p>",
        "ggaeRBqJZKi_text": "<p><i>\"Women can lose up to 20% of their bone mass in the 5-10 years after menopause.” (CDC, 2021)</i></p>",
        "ggc5w6OSulz_text": "<p>I hung up feeling completely trapped. Scared of fractures. Scared of drugs. Scared of not doing anything. Angry that eight years of doing everything right had been completely wasted.</p>",
        "ggeM7MyPmDb_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#045529;\"><i><strong>Osteoblasts </strong></i></span><i>- These build new bone. They're the construction crew.</i></p>",
        "ggembLUrEkb_text": "<p><strong>My doctor's voice was different... Serious.</strong></p>",
        "ggfNWXVnoup_text": "<p>I did yoga three times a week. Took long walks. Lifted light weights.</p>",
        "gggyUO01U5K_text": "<p>Jaw necrosis. Where your jawbone literally dies and rots away.</p>",
        "gghqa4u2EhC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-98984221-2490-4c15-9b73-85987c7e81ac.png",
        "ggiYpjKl7ne_text": "<p><i>\"But before I elaborate, you need to understand something first. You need to know what's really happening inside your bones.\"</i></p>",
        "ggksvtiX5Sl_text": "<p>- Heart issues</p>",
        "gglDOyOnFN9_text": "<p><i><strong>(It's Not What You Think)</strong></i></p>",
        "gglXF4A3wuT_text": "<p>&nbsp;I researched. What I found about bisphosphonates like Fosamax &amp; Prolia made my stomach turn...</p>",
        "gglzsFjW1wz_text": "<p>And the kicker? These drugs don't even build new bone. They just freeze your bone cycle in place.</p>",
        "ggmiBiNQAQk_text": "<p><strong>Late Night Research Led Me To A Doctor Who Finally Told The Truth</strong></p>",
        "ggnfPrN7h7s_text": "<p><i>\"I told myself it wasn't my problem to fix. I could have kept quiet. Kept collecting paychecks. Until it became personal... My own mother became part of the statistics.\"</i></p>",
        "ggnmK6Pz8mQ_text": "<p><strong>And then Dr. Chen explained something my doctor never mentioned.</strong></p>",
        "ggoUrSJ-7I1_text": "<p>So when she recommended a routine bone density scan after I turned 52, I wasn't worried at all.</p>",
        "ggqXVmCbovt_text": "<p>I called my doctor back.</p>",
        "ggqjNmCrefo_text": "<p>That night, I couldn't sleep. I was so frustrated. I kept thinking about my grandmother. How one fall put her in a wheelchair. How she never recovered.</p>",
        "ggqu0YMVRNj_text": "<p>When estrogen drops during menopause, the demolition crew goes into overdrive. No boss to stop them.</p>",
        "ggqye3ounhQ_text": "<p><i>\"The drugs we gave women with osteoporosis never rebuilt bones. Other than very risky anabolic drugs for the worst cases, they just froze the damage. And the side effects? Jaw necrosis. Blood clots. Brittle fractures.\"</i></p>",
        "ggrDFK55829_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-b6701bca-9366-4d82-9a54-daeffe4b594b_1.webp",
        "ggrIoxqAUEe_text": "<p>When you're young, these crews work in perfect balance. Old bone out, new bone in.</p>",
        "ggtCGMMlJ6I_text": "<p><i><strong>\"Why doesn't calcium work for osteoporosis?\"</strong></i></p>",
        "gguDvmNqNNw_text": "<p><strong>But that's not all what shocked me:</strong></p>",
        "ggui5i1GipB_text": "<p><i>\"Sarah, we need to talk about your results.\"</i></p>",
        "ggvNa_8HS6i_text": "<p><strong>\"After 20 Years In Big Pharma, I Finally Admitted The Truth: We Were Treating The Wrong Problem Entirely\"</strong></p>",
        "ggw7nsh5lF3_text": "<p><strong>But I Was About To Become Even More Terrified Of The So-Called Solution...</strong></p>",
        "ggwjmJ7jSRy_text": "<p><strong>But unfortunately, it's not that simple.</strong></p>",
        "ggxNDtRW9qC_text": "<p>I ate yogurt. Drank milk. Loaded up on leafy greens.</p>",
        "ggyFdfybFSs_text": "<p><strong>Estrogen is the boss that keeps the demolition crew in check.</strong></p>",
        "ggzuYDhgsUb_text": "<p>They start tearing down bone faster than the builders can replace it.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607866108799615543"
    },
    "gp_section_607888589312754262": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "26ceb7afcc1fe7a2dc6cd0998cfe6c112b2daaae620381a6b5980c62db87fd80_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1diAmsMHb_text": "<p>Just a simple step down. Her ankle shattered.</p>",
        "gg5IwIIyyke_text": "<p>That was the terrifying part. Then one day, while visiting family, she stepped off a curb.</p>",
        "ggCDnVLNrFf_text": "<p><strong>Together, these 3 ingredients create a complete system:</strong></p>",
        "ggFuZBzz2hs_text": "<p><strong>That's When Dr. Chen Revealed The Real solution.</strong></p>",
        "ggGZSsPpcaW_text": "<p><strong>Dr. Chen became furious.</strong></p>",
        "ggKG3kzicrQ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_c7gbbvc7gbbvc7gb_ddba5816-e417-4342-b9e5-2f3279b045a5.webp",
        "ggR7SuXt7md_text": "<p>2. Activate the bone-builders.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggTSCzGlqMG_text": "<p>Suddenly she couldn't walk without pain. Couldn't do the things that made her feel like herself. Her independence vanished in a single moment.</p>",
        "ggW_gXkr0NI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/applsci-11-08791-g001.webp",
        "ggYmzIMNmMH_text": "<p>Not at his mother. At a system that let this happen. A system that called it \"silent disease\" and then acted shocked when women broke bones from everyday life.</p>",
        "ggaX0UIHvZk_text": "<p>1. Restores energy to the osteoblasts.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggeP0XsBuiO_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-adca4081-72c8-4390-b0c6-6193971e572f.webp",
        "ggfBRLcFa5W_text": "<p><i><strong>\"Not a bad sprain. Not a minor fracture... A complete break from what should have been nothing.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggfHVVw0ftD_text": "<p>And the worst part?</p>",
        "ggjYx5-9pbs_text": "<p>He explained that NAD+ doesn't work alone. You need three things working together: NAD+, Resveratrol &amp; Quercetin.</p>",
        "ggoCXfAjMCa_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1ac8eee2-7a94-4b1d-aada-093f8c512a9d.webp",
        "gguls-ItZR8_text": "<p>This explained everything. The drugs my doctor wanted to prescribe would never actually rebuild my bones.</p>",
        "ggv_zir-gt__text": "<p>They'd just trap them in a state of suspended decay.</p>",
        "ggw2b4bwXal_text": "<p><strong>Dr. Chen's Personal Crisis: The Reason He Left Big Pharma</strong></p>",
        "ggwv586UOXX_text": "<p>3. Calms the osteoclasts.</p>",
        "ggyJK5eVZmv_text": "<p>Her rheumatologist still had no real answers. He prescribed Fosamax and told her to take more calcium.</p>",
        "ggyve-F6dTL_text": "<p><strong>She was devastated. Debilitating. Depressing. Dr. Chen watched his mother's world collapse overnight.</strong></p>",
        "ggz4N5O3-TB_text": "<p>Dr. Chen's mother had no symptoms.</p><p>She felt fine. She thought she was healthy.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607888589312754262"
    },
    "gp_section_607888589547635610": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "d22a98fcc06d9f9d984d342cfce0e8612438e9c18cb42477edbae8df7794ff15_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1VInSjAqI_text": "<p><strong>Okinawan women naturally maintain up to 45% higher levels of this molecule called NAD+ their entire lives.</strong></p>",
        "gg2zFUDE4Av_text": "<p><strong>⚠️ The Dark Side of Calcium</strong></p>",
        "gg3QPAlfDu1_text": "<p>Think of it like the battery that powers all trillion cells in your body.</p>",
        "gg3c7rXHIA9_text": "<p>I sat at my kitchen table at 2 AM, reading this. And I started crying.</p>",
        "gg4cFwssT7x_text": "<p><strong>We can't eat live like Okinawans.</strong></p>",
        "gg5AXhDAlQd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-6f391a7f-698d-4d6b-944e-e2f18276f959.webp",
        "gg5BqC3CDaR_text": "<p><strong>For others… it ends in something far worse.</strong></p>",
        "gg5H_LeJJO2_text": "<p><strong>But here's the kicker:</strong></p>",
        "gg8BW8Grlto_text": "<p>That's why you can take calcium &amp; vitamin D for years and still lose bone density.</p>",
        "gg9W7VMrxmy_text": "<p>They profit off keeping women trapped on medications that only slow damage, never heal it.</p>",
        "ggDK2V330uo_text": "<p><strong>The Discovery That Changed Everything</strong></p>",
        "ggDfWqpRTBU_text": "<p><strong>They've run out of energy.</strong></p>",
        "ggHpcr1IMiU_text": "<p><strong>The result? 40% fewer hip fractures than American women.</strong></p>",
        "ggIuzM6Lj3__text": "<p>Their bone-building cells stay charged, which means their bones stay strong.</p>",
        "ggJrUZ49ox-_text": "<p><i>\"For decades, we told women the problem was calcium deficiency. We were wrong. The problem is cellular energy deficiency.\"</i></p>",
        "ggK1PPOBSNT_text": "<p><strong>The construction crew is exhausted.</strong></p>",
        "ggKL5BF9XlR_text": "<p><i>\"Worse, long-term use &nbsp;can create \"frozen bone\" that becomes brittle. That's why women on these drugs for years still fracture.\"</i></p>",
        "ggLCdxf_X37_text": "<p>For some, that ends in kidney stones.</p>",
        "ggMuibq8iiM_text": "<p>Not sad tears. Angry tears.</p>",
        "ggOIPtBGrH4_text": "<p><i>\"Bisphosphonates like Fosamax slow bone loss by stopping your demolition crew. But they do nothing to build new bone.\"</i></p>",
        "ggSPD1Z0wjI_text": "<p>Dr. Chen realized something important:</p>",
        "ggTVcTbf1s3_text": "<p>And that's exactly why Big Pharma keeps pushing drugs that never fix the real problem.</p>",
        "ggUkYD-Waw5_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-909fbcb6-962f-40b6-9283-459088503cbc.webp",
        "ggVJ-LLabj6_text": "<p>Scientists wanted to know why.</p>",
        "ggVz71yh-uX_text": "<p><strong>Our NAD+ gets drained faster than ever before.</strong></p>",
        "ggWXp_gylzf_text": "<p>The result? 40% fewer hip fractures than American women. But here's the problem for the rest of us.</p>",
        "ggX-7vMhCik_text": "<p><i><strong>But if your construction workers have no energy to pick them up and lay them, nothing gets built.</strong></i></p>",
        "ggYaVq2q5av_text": "<p>The real problem isn't just the demolition crew running wild.</p>",
        "gg_WP8PApQk_text": "<p>Our food supply is polluted with pesticides and toxins. Our stress is higher. Our air quality is worse.</p>",
        "ggaY1Nxymqz_text": "<p>Women there stay strong into their 70s and 80s. They don't live in fear of fractures.</p>",
        "ggahzKgzxOj_text": "<p>When your body has too much calcium... it begins to build up in the blood.</p>",
        "ggcIser-BVu_text": "<p>And as you get older your bone-building cells need massive amounts of it to do their job.</p>",
        "ggcU39R_nFq_text": "<p><strong>If we could restore NAD+ levels directly, we could give the bone-building cells the energy they desperately need.</strong></p>",
        "gggfmV6ftsQ_text": "<p>They eat foods loaded with NAD+, purple sweet potatoes, fermented soybeans, and fresh fish.</p>",
        "ggh32VUcwLQ_text": "<p><strong>Our NAD+ gets drained faster than ever before.</strong></p>",
        "ggi_4MBgF5l_text": "<p><strong>It turns out that the Okinawan women have figured out the secret.</strong></p>",
        "ggih5RT0a13_text": "<p><i>It can lead to deposits in the walls of your arteries, creating calcified blockages which strain your kidneys.</i></p>",
        "ggjbdzjkAKs_text": "<p>Think of calcium like bricks sitting on a construction site.</p>",
        "ggkUqY-sByD_text": "<p>Dr. Chen realized something important:</p>",
        "ggkoiGyV_k__text": "<p><strong>We can't eat like Okinawans.</strong></p>",
        "ggkpCB1iB7-_text": "<p>But then Dr. Chen shared something that gave me hope for the first time in weeks.</p>",
        "gglMVQ0P-my_text": "<p>What they found was shocking:</p>",
        "ggnCTwVJD3Q_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_prhxxpprhxxpprhx.webp",
        "ggrAK7I_Ntz_text": "<p>Dr. Chen's research led him to a small group of islands in Japan.</p>",
        "ggrXP6UgwF6_text": "<p>Dr. Chen explained something that finally made sense of why antiresorptive drugs have such terrible track records:</p>",
        "ggrn0YeqdxU_text": "<p>All the materials in the world won't help if you have no energy...</p>",
        "ggs8Y1PGWfq_text": "<p>NAD+ is an essential coenzyme found in every living cell, that plays a crucial role in cellular function.</p>",
        "ggseMm8b9SO_text": "<p>That's exactly what's happening in your bones.</p>",
        "ggssFmSogO__text": "<p>Our food supply is polluted with pesticides and toxins. Our stress is higher. Our air quality is worse.</p>",
        "ggt7_gQtCxx_text": "<p><strong>Why Drugs Will Never Fix The Real Problem</strong></p>",
        "gguRRAufuRL_text": "<p>They also live in cleaner environments with less pollution. Less oxidative stress draining their cellular energy.</p>",
        "gguWlg5VN2O_text": "<p><strong>Okinawa.</strong></p>",
        "gguwWTKCXxy_text": "<p><strong>You can pile up all the bricks you want.</strong></p>",
        "ggvmhSg1GpI_text": "<p>But here's the problem for the rest of us.</p>",
        "ggw27OJhNWW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/AOI_d_9M7aU46ebT5TCbp6QXpQsU2kVt.webp",
        "ggwQsOmpcFy_text": "<p><strong>Your builders literally don't have the energy to use the calcium and vitamin D you're taking.</strong></p>",
        "ggwjvn_EbHT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-4d7ec6a2-cdb6-4fe0-ac2e-4adaa3b884db.webp",
        "ggwvAH1Ckij_text": "<p><strong>How many years had I wasted? How much bone density had I lost that I could have saved?</strong></p>",
        "ggx3NGoQExj_text": "<p>And this is where calcium completely fails.</p>",
        "ggzp-cwenN__text": "<p><strong>But after age 40, your NAD+ levels drop by up to 50%.</strong></p>",
        "ggzwfbjHOYY_text": "<p><strong>Later Dr. Chen wrote something that made me want to cry:</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607888589547635610"
    },
    "gp_section_607888784247227290": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "8ee675ddd3525534c4c805ff0e36b17249352029575560e78440b8b2a6852ea2_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-H1hry-FF_text": "<p><strong>What Happened In The First 2 Months Surprised Me</strong></p>",
        "gg-s0U6soG1_text": "<p>So he did something radical. He quit his 20-year position at a major pharmaceutical company.</p>",
        "gg57qaWu89q_text": "<p><strong>I woke up without my usual morning stiffness.</strong></p>",
        "gg8pzDZbs5C_text": "<p>For over 2 years, they tested everything. Studied the Okinawan diet. Researched NAD+. Tested formulation after formulation.</p>",
        "gg9OoveVtS4_text": "<p><strong>I'm not going to lie and say it was instant magic.</strong></p>",
        "ggAMeXQS23C_text": "<p>That's why he named their mission Thirmik, literally meaning \"The Small Healer\" in Ancient Greek. A symbol of resistance against corporate medicine.</p>",
        "ggDHHltiLdp_text": "<p><i>\"Last Saturday, little Miko asked me to chase him around the backyard. I actually did it. I jogged. I didn't limp. I didn't hold my breath waiting for pain. I just moved like a normal grandmother.\"</i></p>",
        "ggFvTXY1XMj_text": "<p>I thought about being too scared to pick up my future grandchildren.</p>",
        "ggG_xmYDPZT_text": "<p><strong>He was going to make sure every woman who needed this could actually get it. That's why he spent the last year documenting everything.</strong></p>",
        "ggHr8lIuHuY_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_urn40purn40purn4.webp",
        "ggJehb3Ac6q_text": "<p>The first week, I felt... nothing. I almost gave up.</p>",
        "ggKekNfr3oa_text": "<p><strong>After 47 failed formulations, something changed... His mother called him crying—not from pain. From joy.</strong></p>",
        "ggNGprUED0g_text": "<p><i><strong>\"I think I finally found an answer,\" I told him. \"I'm just scared to hope again.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggPpVnkxLve_text": "<p><i>Dr. Chen made a decision. He wasn't going to keep this in a lab for the wealthy. He was never going to sell it to Big Pharma so they could mark it up 1,000%.</i></p>",
        "ggQsU4z0Vvo_text": "<p>My husband found me sitting there, papers spread across the table.</p>",
        "ggSW2DFaGJk_text": "<p>I could just... stand up. Like a normal person.</p>",
        "ggWWqMTc7aw_text": "<p>But Dr. Chen's mother was his North Star. He tested every breakthrough on her first.</p>",
        "ggWvn2N22-g_text": "<p>I sat at my kitchen table, reading his research papers. Looking at the actual published studies.</p>",
        "ggY03jT1J_N_text": "<p><strong>I thought about my grandmother in that wheelchair.</strong></p>",
        "ggYXdI-yk_g_text": "<p>There were failures. Dead ends. Ingredients that didn't work.</p>",
        "ggYyqjIt5bH_text": "<p><i>\"Then test it. What do you have to lose?\"</i></p>",
        "ggi1bl1QkCJ_text": "<p>At some point, I started crying.</p>",
        "ggi3VcyVkmn_text": "<p>Getting out of bed didn't require the slow, painful roll-and-push routine I'd developed.</p>",
        "ggjfdg7aZ06_text": "<p><strong>Real women. Real results. Published science in peer-reviewed journals.</strong></p>",
        "ggkMRV_xH8L_text": "<p>But around week 3, I noticed something small.</p>",
        "ggl4xBQCUfP_text": "<p>That's when Dr. Chen knew they had it.</p>",
        "ggmjbk6oDPm_text": "<p>He put his hand on my shoulder.</p>",
        "ggo1mYdaXhX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_hsp0fwhsp0fwhsp0.webp",
        "ggq59SEdRoo_text": "<p><i>“What happened?”</i> he asked.</p>",
        "ggq71DIpz19_text": "<p><strong>He called it Thryve.</strong></p>",
        "ggq_ia6MVLE_text": "<p>But he also realized something else: His mother wasn't alone. Millions of women were trapped in the same nightmare...</p>",
        "ggrdlE_zvpK_text": "<p><strong>So I gave myself six months, one last try before accepting defeat.</strong></p>",
        "ggrhb7v8AsY_text": "<p>Dr. Marcus Chen teamed up with three trusted colleagues: Dr. Elena Reid (cellular biologist), Dr. Rowan James (longevity researcher), and Dr. Marcus DeShawn (osteologist).</p>",
        "ggs8jkNaELT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_d7apdhd7apdhd7ap.webp",
        "gguSWW5WkqM_text": "<p>He was right.</p>",
        "ggxGHRLXsSw_text": "<p>I thought about my next bone scan in six months.</p>",
        "ggxbYRwfu2E_text": "<p>Silent disease. No warning. One moment changes everything. Told drugs were their only option, trapped in bodies that felt like they were failing them.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607888784247227290"
    },
    "gp_section_607890080152945238": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "52bd64d371246ed802c43342d35c534a7f5e4f56a27f838eae9d9194d11964e1_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2uOM2116Y_text": "<p><strong>I felt like myself again.</strong></p>",
        "gg3L8tjYKjW_text": "<p>I didn't realize how much fear I'd been carrying until I finally let it go.</p>",
        "gg5bl0rRp3M_text": "<p>I told her about Dr. Chen's research. About NAD+. About restoring cellular energy.</p>",
        "gg6C5BRdUnX_text": "<p><i><strong>She pulled up my scans side by side on the screen. My old scan from August last year. The new one from February.</strong></i></p>",
        "gg8-0fEuMxl_text": "<p>He was right.</p>",
        "gg8SmwssvW__text": "<p>My bones demolition crew was still active, but my bone's construction crew had finally woken up.</p>",
        "gg96mqAe0Vu_text": "<p><strong>I'd been tiptoeing through my own life. Afraid every movement might cause a fracture.</strong></p>",
        "ggBiUz-K9TI_text": "<p>Week 6 is when my husband noticed.</p>",
        "ggCDAKces86_text": "<p><i><strong>\"Sarah, your T-score improved to negative 1.9. You've gained bone density.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggDB1I9aL_1_text": "<p>By month 4, I was doing things I'd stopped doing.</p>",
        "ggIR3RvmLKy_text": "<p>I reached up to get something from the top shelf without that moment of hesitation and mental calculation.</p>",
        "ggJDz23aFfO_text": "<p><strong>I started crying right there in her office.</strong></p>",
        "ggJpsBVUPZe_text": "<p>She was quiet for a moment.</p>",
        "ggKM12xxoUh_text": "<p><strong>By week 5, my knee pain during yoga was noticeably better.</strong></p>",
        "ggM-E8beuwQ_text": "<p><strong>My daughter called and asked if I wanted to help her move furniture for her new apartment.</strong></p>",
        "ggMvDDrWj5B_text": "<p>The physical changes were obvious.</p><p>But the emotional shift was even bigger.</p>",
        "ggPo_4W5CmQ_text": "<p><strong>I was terrified the night before.</strong></p><p><strong>What if nothing had changed? What if I'd just wasted another 6 months?</strong></p>",
        "ggPzHI1G9Ix_text": "<p><strong>She looked genuinely surprised. \"What did you do? What changed?\"</strong></p>",
        "ggS57mEwk1z_text": "<p><strong>I carried a full laundry basket up the stairs. Both hands. No fear.</strong></p>",
        "ggXymGOyI65_text": "<p>Downward dog didn't make my wrists ache. &nbsp;And especially warrior pose didn't make my back throb.</p>",
        "gg_jPC9kyPh_text": "<p>Then my doctor came in to review the results.</p>",
        "ggclCjlNQzk_text": "<p>Then my doctor came in to review the results.</p>",
        "ggdVZ6T6KCh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_83911s83911s8391.webp",
        "gge4L-lMWQ2_text": "<p>My adult son Hunter noticed it during Friday night dinner.</p>",
        "ggg2h2Oweu6_text": "<p>Just... me. Sarah. The person I was before that devastating phone call.</p>",
        "gggSiGoTJmg_text": "<p>That constant fear was starting to lift.</p>",
        "ggh-X0XQIoH_text": "<p>A few months ago, I would have made an excuse. Now I said yes.</p>",
        "ggk5Vsz8shc_text": "<p>What if my hope had been stupid and naive? The next morning, the technician did the scan.</p>",
        "ggkLnIGKx7B_text": "<p><strong>I went from borderline osteoporosis back to moderate osteopenia in record time.</strong></p>",
        "ggmBiSFyXZh_text": "<p>I reached up to get something from the top shelf without that moment of hesitation and mental calculation.</p>",
        "ggmHq7l7r2p_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_hgcxnihgcxnihgcx.webp",
        "ggnBru7aSdU_text": "<p><i><strong>\"Mom, you seem happier,\" he said. \"More like your old self.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggnGPid-ZCD_text": "<p><strong>They had the energy to rebuild again.</strong></p>",
        "ggniS0cZmoY_text": "<p><i>\"How is this possible? You said just keep taking calcium...\"</i></p>",
        "ggpwJ7b0AxK_text": "<p>Not some fragile version of myself. Not some old lady waiting to break.</p>",
        "ggqJ6LI_Yk7_text": "<p><strong>Month 4: The Confidence Started Coming Back</strong></p>",
        "ggtSEizjuf1_text": "<p>I went for a hike with my sister. A real hike with elevation, not a gentle walk on flat ground.</p>",
        "ggu1yA2_MEl_text": "<p><i>\"I don't know much about this approach,\" she admitted. \"But whatever you're doing, keep doing it. This is remarkable for someone your age going through menopause.\"</i></p>",
        "ggvVZ9OaVK1_text": "<p>I could hold poses I'd been modifying for months.</p>",
        "ggykf75_TqX_text": "<p>My follow-up DEXA scan was scheduled for next February.</p>",
        "ggzBs6uolvA_text": "<p><i><strong>\"You're moving differently,\" he said. \"Like you're not scared of your own body anymore.\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggzTe1LCzVm_text": "<p><strong>My Latest DEXA Scan That Made Me Cry</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607890080152945238"
    },
    "gp_section_607891833489457750": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "62fe5902f55b88c40f92a353f8d6e7952dc8986189fae3f2bea1afacf3271d4f_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-Ky6vGwm8_text": "<p>To protect that standard, Thryve is sold exclusively through the official website at Thirmik.com.</p>",
        "gg0FZk4bBKE_text": "<p><strong>Thryve offers you a genuine 90-day trial with your money back if it doesn't deliver.</strong></p>",
        "gg1Tuqb4glh_text": "<p><i><strong>&nbsp;(Before It Sells Out Again)</strong></i></p>",
        "gg4O_K1gq0W_text": "<p><strong>How To Get Thryve</strong></p>",
        "gg5qKG-N7Xn_text": "<p><strong>3.</strong> Word is spreading fast among women who are tired of being told calcium or drugs are their only option.</p>",
        "gg8WDaJAmGQ_text": "<p>She was trained to prescribe the drugs the pharmaceutical reps tell her about. The ones with billion-dollar marketing budgets.</p>",
        "gg8_NqrSxUs_text": "<p><strong>This isn't a quick fix. Your bones didn't weaken overnight. They won't rebuild overnight either.</strong></p>",
        "gg9HhpUAp7t_text": "<p>The science is published. The results are real. The question is whether you're willing to try something your doctor hasn't told you about yet.</p>",
        "ggBqQXn6g0u_text": "<p>They're natural compounds. Anyone can use them. There's no 20-year patent protection. No billion-dollar exclusivity.</p>",
        "ggC8wv5l6aV_text": "<p>But if you give your body the cellular energy it needs for 90 days, you can measure the difference on your next scan.</p>",
        "ggCaoqptmnR_text": "<p><strong>I'm not saying doctors are bad. Mine genuinely didn't know there was another option.</strong></p>",
        "ggCiIyU4ffx_text": "<p><strong>By the time your doctor learns about this, you could lose another 10-20% of your bone mass.</strong></p>",
        "ggFrwrbNV33_text": "<p>Dr. Chen's company offers something no drug company ever would:</p>",
        "ggGPKVzypJa_text": "<p>Here's something Dr. Chen explained in his article that made me angry:</p>",
        "ggHxWAtfoI5_text": "<p><strong>And The Best Part?</strong></p>",
        "ggLZcvaU0Km_text": "<p>Thryve's simple and natural formula works at the cellular level, meaning it won’t interfere with any medications, treatments, or supplements you're currently taking.</p>",
        "ggMCmz09tzE_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1bdfd65c-47bc-4b77-b049-cb3d52d192de.webp",
        "ggONTxCTq8O_text": "<p><strong>2. </strong>Each batch undergoes rigorous testing for purity &amp; quality (adds 2-3 weeks to production).</p>",
        "ggP_Jaaqt9C_text": "<p><strong>NAD+, Resveratrol, and Quercetin can't be patented.</strong></p>",
        "ggQCtovu_KU_text": "<p><strong>Try Thryve for 90 days. If you see 0 improvement in the way you feel or your next bone scan doesn't show improvement, they'll refund every penny.</strong></p>",
        "ggTn0ab66UB_text": "<p>It’s not available on Amazon, eBay, or any third-party marketplaces, because selling direct is the only way they can guarantee proper handling, verified testing, and U.S. manufacturing oversight.</p>",
        "ggU7R4YoONt_text": "<p>When you restore cellular energy, activate bone-building genes, and calm inflammation, your body knows what to do.</p>",
        "ggUKgp06TLp_text": "<p>That's permanent loss. Bone you can never fully regain.</p>",
        "ggVekDk8PlF_text": "<p>So there's no financial incentive for drug companies to research them or for pharmaceutical reps to tell doctors about them.</p>",
        "gg_LKuKoy1S_text": "<p>Right now, they're offering a special bundle for women who want to commit to the full 90-day protocol:</p>",
        "gg_ZsyMABLk_text": "<p><strong>Just like I did. Just like Linda, Jennifer, and Patricia did.</strong></p>",
        "gg_q9K6Y17-_text": "<p><strong>Because of this, they sell out regularly. Not because of artificial scarcity, but:</strong></p>",
        "ggc_zBuCe7t_text": "<p>That's enough for three months. The same timeline that changed everything for me.</p>",
        "ggd8lJcprb7_text": "<p>That's why the breakthrough research on NAD+ and bone health from Harvard Medical School and Stanford is happening right now, but your doctor hasn't mentioned it yet.</p>",
        "ggdCDB6rL3Z_text": "<p>Just three powerhouse ingredients, encased in an easy-to-swallow vegetable capsule. Made right here in the USA and shipped straight to your door.</p>",
        "ggex25Qn53K_text": "<p>Bisphosphonates with no guarantee they'll work. A long list of terrifying side effects. And if they don't work or you can't tolerate them, you're back where you started - but with weaker bones.</p>",
        "ggg2Qr1agE8_text": "<p><strong>1.</strong> Small-batch production in the USA, using premium ingredients takes time.</p>",
        "gggjxH74zj5_text": "<p><strong>It takes 17 years on average for new research to reach mainstream medical practice.</strong></p>",
        "gglM-fjkcrX_text": "<p><strong>Thanks to NAD+, your body actually gains the energy it needs to fully utilize your bone-supporting supplements like calcium, magnesium, vitamin D3, and K2 to their full potential.</strong></p>",
        "ggmPcq9roro_text": "<p>They profit from drugs you take forever. Drugs that manage symptoms but never fix the root cause.</p>",
        "ggm_JdkSO5V_text": "<p>No questions asked. No hassle. No keeping the bottles or jumping through hoops. They can offer this because the science works.</p>",
        "ggnUFwS8AGB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-5b152c85-78d4-4510-bb75-c0dfdb0a78df.webp",
        "ggnYF_Z1inD_text": "<p>Dr. Chen's company produces Thryve in small batches to maintain quality control and ensure every bottle contains exactly what the label promises.</p>",
        "ggrDMipZEL0_text": "<p><strong>Why Your Doctor Probably Won't Tell You About This</strong></p>",
        "ggs0tTHtAvI_text": "<p><strong>The 90-Day Guarantee That Removes All Risk</strong></p>",
        "ggsHWfxFNT9_text": "<p><strong>Big Pharma doesn't profit from helping your body heal itself.</strong></p>",
        "ggtdVtwu-6n_text": "<p><strong>But waiting for the medical system to catch up could cost you your independence.</strong></p>",
        "ggtloRvq-MA_text": "<p>Think about it: What does your doctor's option offer?</p>",
        "gguidrOix3h_text": "<p>Here's what you need to know:</p>",
        "ggvAhZSb5bu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-19c2478b-c6e0-4f75-b8f0-f632bbbc1eb3.webp",
        "ggvCmp6mIbU_text": "<p>That's the difference between a company that profits from keeping you dependent on drugs forever, and a company that stands behind its science.</p>",
        "ggwMAqG6-oz_text": "<p><strong>The only risk is doing nothing and losing more bone mass while you wait for a better option that isn't coming.</strong></p>",
        "ggwTfxSRn8v_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-6ca8e608-320c-4768-9b29-ee8eba4c9af4_1.webp",
        "ggxIk44MJII_text": "<p><strong>Order 2 bottles, get 1 free on them + &nbsp;free shipping.</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607891833489457750"
    },
    "gp_section_607894733984891447": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9ee4246a7ef33b3bfc01a3a6fdb7f3ac40ca483ae1aa127aa49e3a98788794cb_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg7JGwQ3KeA_text": "<p><strong>P.P.S.</strong> - If you're still taking calcium and vitamin D but not seeing results, now you know why. You're giving your body the materials but not the energy to use them. Thryve completes the equation your doctor never explained. The construction workers finally get the power they need to lay those bricks.</p>",
        "ggEdxn8bQmm_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1c5cf179-64bc-415d-b158-d3886355c05c.webp",
        "ggG7U0nxMo5_text": "<p><strong>P.S.</strong> - Remember, you have 90 days to try this completely risk-free. Your money back if you don't feel a difference or your next scan doesn't show improvement. The only way you lose is if you do nothing and your bones keep getting weaker while you wait. Don't let that be your story.</p>",
        "ggJ0IAyr6FI_text": "<p><strong>The 3-Ingredient System That Finally Gave My Bones The Energy To Rebuild</strong></p>",
        "ggUa1h0jaej_text": "<p><strong>P.P.P.S.</strong> - Still not sure? Consider this: What's the real cost of doing nothing? Another year of declining bone density? A fracture that puts you in the hospital? A hip break that means assisted living? Calculate what six months of Thryve costs versus one day in the hospital for a broken hip. The math isn't even close. And unlike the hospital bill, Thryve comes with a money-back guarantee.</p>",
        "ggYrjfgWJme_text": "<p>With the New Year here, now is the perfect time to focus on your bones and start the year by giving them the support they need.</p>",
        "ggbesdd-eiK_text": "<p><strong>Sell out Risk: High</strong></p>",
        "ggnWfiQOlaJ_text": "<p><strong>Click the button below to see if</strong></p><p><strong>Thryve is still in stock and claim their Buy 2, Get 1 Free offer.</strong></p>",
        "ggoE5R3aGdM_label": "<p><strong>CHECK AVAILABILITY</strong></p>",
        "ggsLtz453BL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1c5cf179-64bc-415d-b158-d3886355c05c.webp",
        "ggsLtz453BL_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_to897jto897jto89.webp",
        "ggsa6Rys9HX_text": "<p><strong>Sell out Risk: High</strong></p>",
        "ggwJ4o1GCui_text": "<p>With the current production schedule and testing protocols, Dr. Chen's company can only produce 500 units per month.</p>",
        "ggxTFUYgS2Z_text": "<p><strong>Last month, they sold out in 6 days. The month before, 4 days. I honestly can't guarantee how long this batch will last.</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607894733984891447"
    },
    "gp_section_607894756718019127": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "98cc65537d9ece41abc55801c8c87b50cc33c04683dc9ecd1c4bd57d98537bae_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg26vuP84Or_text": "<p>Today, I cried happy tears. I can't wait to hold my grandchild. To play. To be the active, involved grandmother I always imagined being.</p>",
        "gg5sbcQChCg_text": "<p>A while back, I would have been too stiff to sit in this chair comfortably. Too scared to walk down the three steps to my garden.</p>",
        "ggGCLiZhT0T_text": "<p><strong>A Letter From Sarah, 2 Years Later</strong></p>",
        "ggIb6Vd2dJX_text": "<p>I'm writing this update sitting on my patio, drinking my morning coffee.</p>",
        "ggJlRUqrKg0_text": "<p>Planning trips. Looking forward to grandchildren. Moving through life without fear.</p>",
        "ggKK6rw-Zxs_text": "<p>Before, that news would have filled me with dread. How could I help with a baby when I was terrified of my own fragility?</p>",
        "ggSO3eRjeAf_text": "<p>But it works. And six months from now, you could be sitting where I am.</p>",
        "ggTZdODafrU_text": "<p>P.S. - My next bone scan is in three months. I have a feeling they're going to be even better. My body finally has what it needs to keep rebuilding. This isn't a temporary fix - it's a permanent restoration of what my cells needed all along.</p>",
        "ggV92Sboi_Y_text": "<p>I don't know you. But I know where you are right now because I was there.</p>",
        "ggWPU-e2XdE_label": "<p><strong>CHECK AVAILABILITY</strong></p>",
        "ggaE5Olz7m2_text": "<p>Staring at a bad bone scan. Feeling betrayed. Trapped between bad options.</p>",
        "ggb4dmFBHUn_text": "<p>With strength and hope,<br>Sarah Martinez</p>",
        "ggeotWDGUwA_text": "<p>My daughter called yesterday. She's pregnant. I'm going to be a grandmother.</p>",
        "gggERRDFMgf_text": "<p>I'm telling you there's a third path.</p><p>It requires patience. It requires 90 days of commitment. It requires trusting science that your doctor hasn't learned about yet.</p>",
        "gghZw6IUe1w_text": "<p>That's what restored bone health really means. It's not about numbers on a scan, although those matter.</p>",
        "ggu8Q247RKe_text": "<p>It's about freedom. Confidence. The ability to live fully instead of existing carefully. It's about getting your future back.</p>",
        "ggvDzz-5HGp_text": "<p>But please, don't let fear of hope stop you from trying. I almost did. I'm so grateful I didn't.</p>",
        "ggyJr9sazt1_text": "<p>Or you could still be where you are now. Except with weaker bones. Fewer options. More regret. The choice is yours.</p>",
        "ggzShZ_iUI7_text": "<p>Today, I just got back from a two-mile walk. My husband and I are planning that Italy trip for our 30th anniversary next year.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607894756718019127"
    },
