        "gg31jvjc8Hj_text": "<p>It's about freedom. Confidence. The ability to live fully instead of existing carefully. It's about getting your future back.</p>",
        "ggX_fD2uoXT_label": "<p><strong>CHECK AVAILABILITY</strong></p>"
