        "ggVM9pHwWbU_text": "<p><strong>Rachner, T. D., Khosla, S., &amp; Hofbauer, L. C.</strong> (2011). <i>Osteoporosis: Now and the future. The Lancet, 377</i>(9773), 1276–1287.</p><p>https://www.longdom.org/open-access/postmenopausal-osteoporosis-causes-mechanisms-risks-diagnosis-treatment-and-prevention-guide1103308.html</p>",
