        "ggfjea4JBuA_text": "<p><strong>Eastell, R., et al.</strong> (2022). <i>Pathophysiology of postmenopausal osteoporosis. Journal of Bone and Mineral Research.</i></p><p>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35193674/</p>",
        "gggp-FXha7u_text": "<p><strong>Chen, X., et al.</strong> (2024). <i>Role of androgens in bone metabolism and osteoclast regulation. International Journal of Molecular Sciences, 25</i>(22), 12139.</p><p>https://www.mdpi.com/1422-0067/25/22/12139</p>",
